high_descs: Turn right, walk past the counter and hang a right, then head towards the wash basin across the hallway, and go to the bedroom to your left, then walk to the desk to your right.
Pick up the pen from the table.
Turn around to the doorway and hang a right, then walk straight ahead across the hallway to the bedroom, and go to the box on the bed.
Put the pen into the box.
Pick up the box with the pen in it.
Turn right, go to the doorway, then head towards the wash basin across the hallway, and go to the bedroom to your left, then walk to the desk to your right.
Put the carton box with pen on the top left corner of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a pen box on the desk.

high_descs: Turn right to walk out the kitchen and head right to walk down the passage and turn left to reach the bedroom desk.
Pick up the pen from the table.
Turn right to head out the box and turn right to walk down the passage to enter the box and face the bed.
Put the pen in the box on the bed.
Pick up the box from the bed.
Turn right to walk down the passage to head to the bedroom on the left and reach the desk.
Put the box on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put the pen in the box on the desk.

high_descs: Turn right and exit the kitchen area, then turn right into the hallway, going all the way to the last doorway on the left, towards the desk to the right.
Pick up the pen on the desk.
Exit the box the way you came in, go straight down all the way to the bedroom far ahead.
Place the pen inside the box on the bed.
Pick up the box with the pen in it.
Return to the desk where you picked up the pen.
Place the box on the desk you picked the pen up from.
anns.task_desc: Place a pen in a box on the bedroom desk.
